Package org.aludratest.app.excelwizard

Class Summary
ClassNameCellRenderer Renders the name of a Java class.
CLIExcelCreator Creates Excel documents for AludraTest classes from the command line.
ExcelSettingsPane Main pane of the ExcelWizard.
ExcelWizard Main class of the Excel wizard.
JavaBeanExcelDocumentMapper Creates and updates Excel documents that match the annotations and data structure of a test method.
MethodNameCellRenderer Renders the names of Methods as list cells.
MethodSelector Lists the test methods of a class which have a Source annotation.
TestClassList Displays a list of test classes and filters them accordings to the settings imposed by TestClassList.updateFilter(String).
WizardUtil Provides utility methods for AludraTest's wizards.
WorkbookTracker Encapsulates data needed for synchronizing and validating Excel documents that provide test data to an AludraTest test method.
